data.description: Just like new but with so many extras in one of Greenbrier’s desirable subdivisions!  Features include granite countertops throughout, sit down vanities in both bathrooms, large lot with outbuildings, tankless water heater and back deck/covered patio perfect for relaxing!  Recent updates include addition of 18x24 metal shop in backyard, attached garage turned into game room with mini split, garage floor coating and new insulated garage door.  Call to see it today!
